  "text": "Recombinant DNA manipulations were carried out in E. coli strain TOP10 (Invitrogen), which was cultured at 37℃ in LB medium. pPICZαA-WT and pPICZαA-I66Q were constructed, and E. coli and P. pastoris strain were transformed with these plasmids as described in our previous work [CITATION_1] .",
